				<li>At max , <b>2 cards</b> can be <b>REVEALED</b> , which counts <b>1 TURN</b> .</li>
				<li>If revealed cards forms a <b> PAIR</b>  , it's a <b> SUCCESS</b>  , awarding <b> 5 points </b> for each success.</li>
				<li>For each <b> UNSUCCESSFUL</b>  turn , <b> 1 mark</b>  will be deducted.</li>
				<li>If they don't , both cards will be hidden again.</li>
				<li>Maximum achieveable score is <b>60</b>,but I <b>BET</b> u can't score that,just because distributon is <b>COMPLETELY RANDOM</b>.....try yourself</li>
